  "remarks": "Apprehended in July 2004 and in custody for trial in the United States of\nAmerica, as at October 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008)\nwas concluded on 21 Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
